{
  "stem": "12447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I never attended any classes after that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She tried to give me some lessons in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my father started to work as a glazier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was like a, a handyman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Actually, he was an iron worker, and he was a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he was kind of versatile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was good, almost like a jack-of-all-trades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So he figured out that, at the time, fixing panes and windows would be the best deal that he could make because it was coming to winter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was-- people had to close in their apartments.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he got himself a big box, I remember, with glass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a diamond cutter that he used.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was helping him out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took that big box on his back, walking around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would come just like a, a, you know, like a peddler, get over to the court of a building and start screaming, 'glazier' and 'glazier' in Polish.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people would call him in and have him fix their windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was quite busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to help him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I even have a scar till today that I tried to cut a piece of glass, and the glass broke and probably cut my vein or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I couldn't-- I couldn't stop bleeding-- I couldn't stop bleeding from my-- from my finger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But nevertheless, I think I did a pretty good job helping him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we used to get up in the morning and go and fix glass as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also, he was able to fix broken locks that people had that-- you know, people broke into their apartments.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had broken doors and broken locks.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
